name: 尼科拉·凯莱赫
name_full: 尼科拉·凯莱赫 Nicola Kelleher
introduction: Nicola is an English actress born in Paddington to Irish parents. Nicola plays Gemma Dorman in Netflix series "Stalkers Who Kill" She is also known for her roles as Sybil in The Smoke and Sharice in "Welcome to Curiosity" Nicola works as a TV Presenter and has worked all over the world making documentaries for Animal Planet and independent TV companies.
